google_play_reviews.content: My device is running on Android 9 and I tried to backup notes, no matter how many times I try, the backup was never successful. Update 1: Thanks for your response. My issue has been resolved. I kept the Notes app running in the background and used Backup application to backup notes data and it was succeeded. Thanks team for such a great app.
google_play_reviews.replyContent: If you wish, you can reach out to us at pfa@secuso.org. That way we may be able to provide you more tailored help. If you reach out please provide us with a bit more information on which version of the apps you are running, where you downloaded them and maybe a screenshot of the error message.
